title: I click launch and then nothing happens
body: I click Launch and nothing happens - It's not my HD or my SSD. I had it on both and nothing happened. It's not my anti-virus (i uninstalled/paused protection etc). My firewall is fine. I seriously have no idea what could be wrong, it started happening after 6.18; and yes, I have submitted a ticket.

replies.body:
If you've already submitted a ticket, then I recommend hanging on while a tech specialist gets back to you.

With the logs you've provided, they'll have a lot more context as to what's going on and how to resolve this. Let me know if you have any other questions.
